    public class LocalDateFixedYearMonthChooser
extends javafx.scene.control.Control
    A control which allows to select a LocalDate for a fixed YearMonth. TODO: Useful as a public API? (e.g. for skinning?) Or should it be hidden as an implementation detail?
    Author:
    puce
